msgctxt "Languages::faq_page.details_notes"
msgid "FAQ details notes"
msgstr "After you create questions here, you should use the <strong>Layout editor</strong> to add them to the storefront.<br /><br />
Go to <a href=\"[layouts_href]\" target=\"_blank\">Design â†’ Layouts</a>, switch to the location where you want the FAQs to appear, and add a new block with type <strong>FAQ</strong>.<br /><br />
In this block settings, go to the <strong>Content</strong> tab, pick the <strong>Manual</strong> filling, and click on the <strong>Add questions</strong> button.<br /><br />
You will see the list of all the questions in your store. Pick the one(s) you need and click on the <strong>Add questions and close</strong> button.<br /><br />
Finally, click on the <strong>Create</strong> button to save your changes.<br /><br />
In addition the FAQ page with list of <strong>all questions</strong> on the storefront can be found <a href=\"/faq-page\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.<br/>
You can add a link to this page through the <strong>Menu Editor</strong> (do not forget to first remove or disable the demo questions added  with the addon)."

